   Actor Tony Randall says a $100,000 gift from
Eagle Snacks Inc. isn't peanuts: he plans to use the money to turn
a rundown movie house into a home for a classical repertory group.
   ``It will take a lot of work and a lot of money, but I think
that this donation from Eagle Snacks will help stimulate the
participation we need to bring great theater back to 42nd Street,''
