<TEXT>
   Six soldiers died Saturday when the
stolen vehicle they were in swerved off a road and plunged into a
river, police said.
   The accident took place before dawn in the town of Puente Duero,
a few miles outside the north-central city of Valladolid. The
driver apparently lost control of the Land-Rover as he approached a
