<HEAD>Three Seized in Botched Australian Bank Job</HEAD>
<DATELINE>SYDNEY, Australia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Three men, two dressed as women, fled
from a Sydney bank Friday after a swindle attempt failed but all
